Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:10.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese language: Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:11.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Math: Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:00:13.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Geography and history: Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:16.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You have a real knack for \Nstupidity, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.18,0:00:18.04,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:21.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,How did you score a zero in English \Nwhen you've lived in England?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:21.35,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,English
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:24.39,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly have you \Nbeen studying up till now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:25.52,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Art.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:27.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What about math and science?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:28.47,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I've never studied those.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.66,0:00:32.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There's no saving this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.65,0:00:36.17,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you've got it rough right \Nfrom the first day of summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.17,0:00:37.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-san, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:38.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Her makeup exams are tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:40.97,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but she's not ready at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:42.07,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What about Chihiro-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.07,0:00:44.39,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She left it up to me and \Nwent to a mixer instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:46.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,And Shiina isn't even worried about it—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.41,0:00:46.94,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.36,0:00:49.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What did I just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:52.91,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I need to do some storyboards \Nfor a serialized manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:55.55,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,My goal is to have them ready \Nby next month's meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.55,0:00:57.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Did Ayano-san tell you to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:58.10,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.10,0:01:00.63,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'd better pass \Nthose makeup exams quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:04.08,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:05.96,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:07.47,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you come in from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.47,0:01:09.38,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,My own personal elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:12.12,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can come directly to this \Nroom without using the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.12,0:01:14.36,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Convenient and comfortable, \Nit's a victory for technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.36,0:01:15.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,And how do you get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.07,0:01:18.80,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this you're \Ndoing behind my back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:20.72,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.72,0:01:22.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We're helping Shiina \Nwith her makeup exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.78,0:01:24.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai, why don't you help out?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.74,0:01:25.71,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Just memorize the info.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.71,0:01:26.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:28.07,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's the only way...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.07,0:01:28.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:31.42,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,The music and art makeup exams...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:33.28,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,are the same as the original test.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:35.43,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike General Studies students,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.43,0:01:39.01,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the school has different \Nexpectations for art students.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:41.90,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro-chan, you got a sample \Nanswer sheet, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.90,0:01:42.66,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:44.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You say to memorize the answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:46.59,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but she can't do it in a day—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:47.29,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I've memorized them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:48.42,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:50.33,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I only have to see them \Nonce to memorize them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:52.03,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine them as pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.85,0:01:57.37,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Who was the ancient Egyptian \Npharaoh who rejected polytheism?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:01:58.70,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Amenhotep IV.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:02.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What is the formula to \Nsolve quadratic equations?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:05.54,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,X equals minus b, plus or\N minus the square root...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:07.69,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,of b squared minus \N4ac, divided by 2a.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:10.38,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Startling...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:12.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This almost smells like a scam...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:15.45,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you're finished now, let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:17.70,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have a makeup-passing party!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:19.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't passed the exams yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:21.82,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay! Mashiron, \Ntake this, hold on, and push!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:23.08,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I've never played a game before...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:26.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just go along with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.39,0:03:58.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:01.47,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Their level of focus is extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:03.68,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,If they're not careful, \Nthey'll stay up all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:07.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I lost to Shiina even \Nthough she's never played before...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:10.52,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're not going home, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Given the situation, \NI don't think I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:16.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro-sensei told me \Nto look after Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:20.03,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm staying, too. I haven't\Nfinished my new script yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.54,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll do everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:24.24,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just throw it all away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:29.18,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to \Ndo over summer break?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:32.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a game development \Naudition in a magazine,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.77,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm hoping to finish my pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:41.54,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:42.80,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:43.81,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think \Nyou're doing in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:46.76,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're \Nboth into gay stuff like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:48.84,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,pouring your sweet nectar \Ndown each others' throats!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:49.68,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,Nectar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:53.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't say weird \Nthings like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:54.86,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun, it's time for revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:55.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:57.87,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna let Mashiron beat you like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:59.00,Saku-overlap,SOIRATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:04:59.00,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You call yourself a man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.72,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Jin! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:01.74,Saku-overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Her makeup exams start tomorrow morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:02.21,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:03.08,Saku-overlap,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:10.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fall asleep during your test.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you in the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:14.19,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:19.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It'll probably take about three hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:20.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:21.21,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,You Have One New Message.\NOne Missed Call
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:25.26,Saku-thought,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, you said you'd \Ncome home over summer break!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:26.64,Saku-thought,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Why haven't you called me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:28.20,Saku-thought,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't decide to come home,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:30.13,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,my summer vacation \Nplans will be ruined—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:30.89,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Play\NStop
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:33.35,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap. I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:41.02,Sign,MAGAZINE,0000,0000,0000,,Go for the Game Grand Prize!\NFujisawa Kazuki
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:44.00,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.82,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:49.49,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Shiina's taking makeup \Nexams, so I tagged along.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:50.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just passing the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:52.33,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,She still needs someone to chaperon her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:54.76,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's been four months \Nsince she arrived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:57.52,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just say we're doing \Nsome dorm buddy bonding...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:58.25,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:00.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:03.08,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I was asked to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:04.63,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You were? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:06.97,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I was late paying my rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.94,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they'd contact my parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:10.86,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,if I was late again this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:11.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.61,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:15.64,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I got some more work, \Nso as of next month...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:18.16,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why {\i1}now{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:18.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.99,0:06:19.40,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:21.73,Sign,SNACK,0000,0000,0000,,Baumkuchen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It was a snack for Shiina, \Nbut you're welcome to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:24.28,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'm on a diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:26.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Call it payback for the chikuwa \Nyou gave me the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:28.46,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I said I don't want—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:31.74,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:36.16,Sign,PHONE,0000,0000,0000,,Alarm: Convenience Store
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.73,0:06:36.16,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to go to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:39.92,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you back for the \Nbaumkuchen once they pay me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:40.87,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:43.45,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:46.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are your exams over?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You should apologize to all \Nthe students of the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:52.89,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,who actually study...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:54.07,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:55.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sound like you mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:56.31,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:58.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it a question now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:07:00.50,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, there are people in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:01.73,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,who work hard and still struggle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.60,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:06.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, Jin-san isn't a struggling student...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:11.45,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Jin must also have makeup exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:14.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,His grades are excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:16.69,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's already been \Nreferred to our college.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.38,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he came to do the \Npaperwork for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:21.36,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:22.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:25.89,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I want Hashimoto Bakery's \Nultimate melon bun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:26.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:31.68,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro said you'd buy me\N one if I passed my exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:34.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't informed of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.08,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.07,Sign,SIGN (top left to bottom right),0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Wada: Off\NAoyama: On Break\NSuzuki: Afternoon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:47.88,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for surprising you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:49.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're not \Npushing yourself too hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:52.99,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. I just felt \Na little lightheaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:56.10,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,See? I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:58.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama, if you're really in trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:01.33,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,can't you ask your parents \Nto send you some money?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:03.21,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:05.76,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a reason you can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:09.03,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, my parents are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:11.85,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,opposed to me studying \Nto be a voice actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.85,0:08:13.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Especially my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:17.47,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,They let me start school \Non the condition that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:19.62,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I pay for my living expenses...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:21.47,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,without relying on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:24.49,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,If the school contacts them, \NI'm certain they'll haul me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:27.01,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,So, I can't ask them for money...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:29.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why don't you come to Sakura Hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:30.15,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:32.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit run down, but the rent's cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:36.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's been more lively since \NI brought all the cats back,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:39.33,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I bet they'd be happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:41.98,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:45.29,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I hadn't even thought about it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:48.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little loud, but it's not \Nthat bad once you get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:50.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,And the room next to Shiina's is free.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.95,0:08:51.75,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:52.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:54.63,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you call me by my first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:55.47,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:56.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:57.39,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Call her by her first name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:59.31,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you to call me Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:00.63,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want strangers to overhear us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:03.00,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and get suspicious about our relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.63,0:09:03.00,Saku-overlap,NAMAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Your relationship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:04.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:05.48,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Use my first name when it's just us two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:06.90,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just the two of us right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:07.53,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.53,0:09:09.09,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Should I be suspicious \Nabout your relationship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:10.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:11.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Someone's already \Ngot the wrong idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:12.40,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:14.19,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:17.61,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't let me \Nsleep a wink last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:18.23,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:20.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No! Like I said, you've got the wrong idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:22.12,Saku-overlap,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, you weren't any good, \Nbut you did it again and again—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:22.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.15,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, {\i1}you{\i0} shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:25.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:27.12,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,We were at it all night, \Nso my body's aching now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:30.57,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,K-K-Kanda-kun! I don't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:31.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No! A game!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.34,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We were playing video games until morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:36.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It was her first time, but for some \Nreason, she was really good at it—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:37.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! Please wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:39.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, I'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:40.64,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:42.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it, Aoyama-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:44.21,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wondering this for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:45.95,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.95,0:09:46.91,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:48.25,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,She told you to use her first name!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:50.12,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,And you said something \Nabout an "owner" for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:54.17,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but Shiina-san went on a \Ndate with Mitaka-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:56.38,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,And after that, I went to \Na love hotel with Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:59.53,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Though, I ended up spending\N the night with Sorata...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:02.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and decide if you're going\N to sleep or stay awake, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:03.11,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:04.73,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,We're high school students!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:07.49,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't have anything \Nto do with d-d-debauchery!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:09.39,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, there's an \Nexplanation for all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:11.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina, say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:14.69,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This is where you should wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:16.02,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:18.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's your idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:22.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll move to Sakura Hall \Nand find out for myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.29,0:10:23.97,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,if I have really got the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:27.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I've got one of Hashimoto Bakery's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:29.19,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,ultimate melon buns right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:31.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you this melon bun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:32.98,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,if you can promise me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:34.05,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:35.57,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't told you what\N the promise is yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:38.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Aoyama will be moving \Ninto Sakura Hall soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:42.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, she'll see \Nhow we act every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:44.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I wake you up in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:45.54,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I put out your clothes for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.17,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I do your laundry and feed you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:49.35,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I even wash, fold,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:50.84,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and pick out your panties for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:51.88,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If she finds out about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:54.10,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,who knows what that serious \NAoyama will think...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:55.80,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat the ultimate melon bun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:59.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I bet that's all you're \Nthinking about right now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:00.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:02.55,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, she'll be convinced \Nthat we're total perverts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:05.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want you to promise that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:08.03,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll take care of \Nyourself from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:08.60,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:10.41,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You just want to eat \Nthe bun, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:14.15,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just\N tell her you're dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:15.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of warped logic is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:19.15,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,If you're lovers, there's \Nnothing strange about...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:21.24,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you washing Mashiro-chan's underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:23.07,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Even Aoyama-san would accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:26.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Brilliant idea, Jin-san. \NYou're a genius—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:27.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:30.31,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You don't usually go in for sarcasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:32.37,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I understand what you're trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:33.49,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:35.09,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Put simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:36.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:38.71,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,...in order to protect our secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:41.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to make \Nit sound so suggestive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:42.22,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,...you want me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:43.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:44.60,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,...to annihilate Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:48.77,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, just tell her you're dating!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.16,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Annihilate her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:52.16,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, a warrior? A soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:53.27,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We'll call your idea Plan B, Jin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use my idea as Plan A.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:57.32,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Annihilating her will be Plan C.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:01.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:01.60,Saku-overlap,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:04.24,Sign,TRUCK,0000,0000,0000,,Rhinoceros Removals
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:05.82,Sign,TAG,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:08.32,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Now I just have to unpack everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:09.13,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:12.17,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:15.17,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:17.10,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.74,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's so nice you all got to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:26.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama, what's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:27.85,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:31.70,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop! Kamiigusa-senpai, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:30.70,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm helping!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:32.74,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to play hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:34.05,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:36.00,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Nanamin wears things like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:38.39,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,The more serious they seem,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:40.71,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the wilder they are in \Nplaces we can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:42.86,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,My friend from back \Nhome gave them to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:44.46,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,as a joke for my birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:45.94,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I've never worn them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.94,0:12:48.12,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she even has one of {\i1}these{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:49.93,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,My friend gave me that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:51.87,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend has good taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:54.15,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,They're so easy to take off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:57.29,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,This is cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.22,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:12:58.88,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:00.40,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's my best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:01.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,"Best friend"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:02.57,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:05.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You did it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:07.00,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,The tea spilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:09.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You mean {\i1}you{\i0} spilled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:12.38,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun! Mitaka-senpai! \NClose your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:12.89,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:15.00,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina-san, you need to \Nget changed quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.35,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:18.65,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:22.33,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:25.12,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,So, she's seen the truth already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:29.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you don't realize it yet, \Nbut Shiina's from another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:34.37,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I figured she was unique, but I \Ndidn't think she was {\i1}this{\i0} odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:38.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Truth is, she can't \Ntake care of herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:40.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's a master painter, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.16,0:13:42.42,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's even making her \Ndebut as a manga artist,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:45.88,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda: Mashiro Duty
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:44.17,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:46.73,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you were talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.89,0:13:49.09,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:50.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you would—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:52.21,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:53.35,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, who could?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:55.76,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how unusual your upbringing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:57.85,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you should be able to \Ntake care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:13:59.28,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I think there's a major problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:01.72,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,with letting a boy do all \Nher laundry and cleaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:03.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But, the other females in Sakura Hall...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.96,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,are a lazy teacher and an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:07.16,Saku-main,NAMAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're forgetting someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:07.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:12.08,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, I will \Nbe on Mashiro Duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:18.58,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Sakura Hall Meeting Minutes{\b0}\NThe person on Mashiro Duty has changed.\NBy majority vote, Aoyama Nanami \Ntakes over Kanda Sorata's duties.\NIs this good enough for the minutes?\N-Aoyama Nanami, Secretary
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:16.35,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Nanamin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:18.58,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be cheering you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:20.08,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama: Mashiro Duty
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:20.08,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:21.04,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:21.96,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're putting in too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.20,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,This is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:26.63,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You can use a computer just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:28.51,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Because that's necessary to draw manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.09,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Laundry is necessary, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:32.36,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:34.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're working multiple jobs,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:37.89,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and you're attending a training school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:39.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You can't add Mashiro Duty to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:42.10,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. I've got it all worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:44.19,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I explain it to her, \NI'm sure even Shiina-san can—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:45.73,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:49.28,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just push random buttons!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:52.13,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:55.91,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,If you turn on a faucet, \Nyou have to turn it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.12,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami, you're going to catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:04.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're walking the same path I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:06.08,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you, I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:13.28,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You saw, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:14.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:15.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:17.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! You have the look \Nof someone who saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:19.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,And what kind of look is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:23.83,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:24.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:25.29,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Fold these.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:27.72,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't ask boys to \Ndo things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:28.97,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't help her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:29.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:31.49,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:33.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's my game pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:36.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I've been writing it over summer break,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:37.98,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I was thinking of submitting \Nit to a development audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:39.83,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:42.49,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:44.37,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it's even more \Nimportant that you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:46.09,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get in Kanda-kun's way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:50.86,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:54.61,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Shiina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:44.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes down to it,\N Aoyama and Shiina...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:46.64,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,look like they're getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:51.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe girls really do get \Nalong better with other girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:55.53,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thanks to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:58.41,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I finished my pitch \Nsooner than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:01.27,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: How does this look for a pitch?\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: I just finished reading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:00.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, there he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:01.91,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: How does this look for a pitch?\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: I just finished reading it.\N{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: What did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:04.44,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: I will say that your idea is interesting.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: In all honesty, in terms of form, \Nit's nowhere near good enough for the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:10.43,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: I will say that your idea is interesting.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: In all honesty, in terms of form, \Nit's nowhere near good enough for the audition.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: It definitely won't make it past screening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:12.43,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: I will say that your idea is interesting.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: In all honesty, in terms of form, \Nit's nowhere near good enough for the audition.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: It definitely won't make it past screening.\N{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: You sure don't beat around the bush.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:16.28,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,I will explain things in very \Nsimple terms so that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:18.58,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,even your disappointment \Nof a brain can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:21.67,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,You must first establish your concept,\N your target, and the benefits,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:23.82,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm not sure that first\N sentence was necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:26.01,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,explaining your content \Nas clearly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:30.90,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Concept
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:29.07,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,Your concept is how you plan to invoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:30.97,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the kind of enjoyment you're aiming for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:33.07,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Target
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:34.03,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,Your target is the age and sex \Nof your intended audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:34.03,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:35.71,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,The benefits are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:36.78,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this all in at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:39.84,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,I'm outlining the most basic \Nof basic elements here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:42.75,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,Is even this too difficult \Nfor you, Sorata-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:45.03,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to phrase it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:50.15,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: You're as technical as I'd expect someone \Nwho actually works in the game industry to be.\N{\b1}Kanda Sorata{\b0}: To be honest, I may have underestimated this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:51.19,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: You're naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:52.69,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: You're naive.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: Stop thinking like a high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:54.19,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: You're naive.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: Stop thinking like a high school student.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: The people evaluating your work are\N adults who make hundreds of millions of yen on games.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:55.51,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: You're naive.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: Stop thinking like a high school student.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: The people evaluating your work are\N adults who make hundreds of millions of yen on games.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: This isn't a kids' game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:58.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,How much more salt are you \Ngoing to rub in the wound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:17:59.62,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: Oh, and one more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:02.62,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: Oh, and one more thing...\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: You should include images.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:03.62,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: Oh, and one more thing...\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: You should include images.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: It'll make your pitch much\N more appealing than reams of endless text.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:05.12,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: Oh, and one more thing...\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: You should include images.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: It'll make your pitch much\N more appealing than reams of endless text.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: Signing off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:06.60,Sign,PC,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: Oh, and one more thing...\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: You should include images.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: It'll make your pitch much\N more appealing than reams of endless text.\N{\b1}Akasaka Ryunosuke{\b0}: Signing off now.\NRyunosuke-sama has logged out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:14.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's a complete failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.49,Sign,NOTEBOOK,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}Concept\NEnjoyment\NPlan\N\NTarget\NTarget Age\NTarget Sex
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.49,Sign,NOTEBOOK,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}Corrections\NInclude Images\NAsk Misaki-senpai...\N\NProblems\NImages? — Think hard!\NColor?\NExplain... how?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.39,0:18:30.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Shiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:32.67,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:35.55,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "what?"! \NWhat are {\i1}you{\i0} doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:36.69,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.69,0:18:38.39,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep in your own room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:40.44,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami would come to \Nwake me up in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:43.90,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been working on \Nyour storyboards until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:44.78,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:47.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sleep! This isn't good, Shiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:48.05,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.05,0:18:48.69,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:50.22,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,When it's just the two \Nof us, call me Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.22,0:18:52.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:54.24,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:00.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making any progress \Non your storyboards?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:02.11,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been getting enough sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:05.56,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:07.62,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're not making any progress?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:09.21,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:11.94,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina... I mean, Mashiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:14.90,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,when is the magazine featuring \Nyour debut going to be published?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:16.00,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,On the 10th...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:18.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to go buy it together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:24.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:26.85,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time your \Nmanga will be in print.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.94,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I knew this would happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:42.50,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:54.20,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun, I knew you \Nwere after my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:54.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:56.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I was stupid to trust you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:57.42,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:19:59.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down! Look at the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:00.17,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.43,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You snuck into a girl's room to—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:04.77,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:06.63,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:08.25,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:09.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:12.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you sleeping\N down here, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:15.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like I'd fall asleep \Nif I went back to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:17.33,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I have a presentation \Nat my training school,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:19.10,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I need to memorize my lines...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:20.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,When's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:21.57,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,The 10th.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:22.82,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The 10th?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:25.70,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have time for Mashiro Duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:28.29,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I've still got a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:30.83,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn to clean this week!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.12,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I need to put out the garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:33.50,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.77,0:20:35.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:39.39,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! It'll only take a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.39,0:20:41.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You should accept the \Nkindness of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:45.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you being so \Nstubborn about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:46.88,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not being stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:49.39,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who should \Nstop being so forceful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:50.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:54.45,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I can do everything myself, \Nso you don't need to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:56.84,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:20:59.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,How can someone who fell \Nasleep down here say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:02.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're pushing yourself too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:03.66,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:05.74,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I slept just fine, so it's no big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:07.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! Do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:08.16,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:10.81,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:13.51,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate the thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.51,0:21:15.82,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I just went three \Nrounds with Rumi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:17.13,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:19.17,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:22.63,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're both getting in the way \Nof my cleaning, so just get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:24.84,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Senpai, you should stop \Nignoring the rules about curfews
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:26.11,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and permissions to stay out late!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:27.47,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:28.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:29.52,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:32.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry you got caught up in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:35.19,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I never could've said all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:39.55,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Asking someone who's so \Nstubborn why they're being...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.55,0:21:40.69,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:42.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Were you listening again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:44.96,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to make up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:47.17,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:51.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Shiina's sleeping \Nin my room right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:52.37,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I was wondering if—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:53.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:57.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I supposed to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.31,0:22:04.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it doesn't matter. \NIt's morning already...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:07.89,Eptitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,#05 The Serious Girl of Sakura Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:34.13,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Youth is synonymous with hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:41.06,NextEptitle,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,#06 The Blue After the Rain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.13,0:23:36.48,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you mess up, you can just \Ndrink and puke, drink and puke,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:38.57,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend you forgot \Neverything that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.57,0:23:41.06,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mister, give me a Hoppy. \NHeavy on the shochu.
